blog.name: looseartist
blog.title: Tanja Jeremić
blog.description: Tanja Jeremić is visual artist based in Belgrade, Serbia. She creates digital collages and motion graphics by combining old photos she finds with contemporary styles. Her work is mainly composed of few unrelated elements from old photographs in which she recognises her thought. She filters those photographs through her personal designs and aesthetics thus giving us her surreal universe.

summary: I finished this lovely commission for Durotos over on deviantart of Claire and Cliff. If you’re interested in commissioning me,...
caption:
I finished this lovely commission for Durotos over on deviantart of Claire and Cliff.

If you’re interested in commissioning me, you can do a ko-fi commission which can be as low as $3, I will draw you chibi characters or create a personalized text for you. Follow the link for more rules and info.

https://ko-fi.com/darianknappart

If you want a more elaborate piece, you can commission me via PayPal. We can negotiate prices and what you want through my email darian_knapp_art@yahoo.com. You pay half before starting your commission and then pay other half upon completion.

http://paypal.me/DarianKnapp
